items.title: Darkest Miriam
items.description: Miriam Gordon lives in a fog of grief while working in a downtown public library branch. When a burgeoning love-affair coincides with her receiving a series of oddly threatening letters, Miriam's sheltered existence is cracked open.

items.title: Mr Doom
items.description: Jack and Charlie are an unlikely pair on a dangerous path to self destruction in a world of their own design. Both struggling to keep up a bygone lifestyle that revolves around a green felt table with six pockets and sixteen balls.

items.title: Family Before Everything
items.description: In the streets of the Cold Springs area of Buffalo, NY, some people provide for their families by any means, making decisions that could end up hurting them in the long run.

items.title: Rule Breakers
items.description: In a nation where educating girls is rebellion, a visionary woman sparks hope and opposition. Their courage ignites a movement that could transform their nation forever.

items.title: Norman's Rare Guitars Documentary
items.description: This world-renowned institution is where legends jam, and find inspiration. This documentary chronicles the shop's unique spirit, as Norman Harris, its beloved founder, faces retirement, marking a turning point for this cultural haven.

items.title: Bob the Builder on Site: Roads and Bridges
items.description: Join Bob and his Can-Do Crew as they explore real life consruction sites! See diggers, mixers and trucks work together to build roads and bridges. From the first hole to the final asphalt cover, Bob the Builder teaches you everything you need to know.鈥擜nonymous
items.rel_title: Bob the Builder on Site: Roads and Bridges.1080p.web.[YTS]

items.title: Seconds to Spare
items.description: When a deadly assassin hijacks a passenger train, he threatens to detonate a deadly can of poison that can wipe out an entire city, if he isn't given a 25 million dollar Ransom. While the cops are attempting to thwart the madman, they decide to call Former DEA agent Paul Blake (Antonio Sabato, Jr) the one man who can possibly stop the fiendish plot.鈥擲peed_n_up

items.title: The Ritchie Blackmore Story
items.description: Documentary about legendary guitarist Richie Blackmore, who is best known for his work with rock bands Rainbow and Deep Purple.

items.title: A Working Man
items.description: Levon Cade left his profession behind to work construction and be a good dad to his daughter. But when a local girl vanishes, he's asked to return to the skills that made him a mythic figure in the shadowy world of counter-terrorism.

items.title: The Woman in the Yard
items.description: A mysterious woman repeatedly appears in a family's front yard, often delivering chilling warnings and unsettling messages, leaving them to question her identity, motives and the potential danger she might pose.

items.title: Not Just a Goof
items.description: A documentary exploring the untold story of A Goofy Movie (1995). It follows a young creative team tackling their first Disney feature, its initial disappointment, and its surprising resurgence decades later.

items.title: Pets
items.description: It explores the extraordinary relationship between animals and their people around the world. Highlighting dogs, cats, pigs, goats, and birds of prey, Pets takes us on a lovely journey that celebrates love, loss, and licks along the way.

items.title: iHostage
items.description: When a gunman enters an Apple Store in the heart of Amsterdam, the police face a delicate challenge to resolve the standoff. Based on true events.

items.title: Dead Mail
items.description: An ominous help note finds its way to a 1980s post office, connecting a dead letter investigator to a kidnapped keyboard technician.

items.title: Everybody Loves Touda
items.description: Touda is a Sheikha, a traditional Moroccan singer. Performing in the bars of her provincial town under the gaze of men, she plans to leave for the lights of Casablanca, to gain recognition and ensure a better future for her son.

items.title: Meet the Khumalos
items.description: Two moms- once best friends turned enemies- go to war when the find out their children are madly in love.

items.title: Reversi
items.description: A man's undying love for his wife and son makes him go to great lengths to correct his past for a better future.

items.title: Unmarried Couples: A Comedy That Will Break You Up
items.description: Marie and David are always arguing while their friends Sara and Samuel always seem to be happy together. Or are they? This year they decide to spend Christmas in the mountains together.
items.rel_title: Unmarried Couples: A Comedy That Will Break You Up.1080p.web.[YTS]

items.title: September Says
items.description: When September is suspended from their school, her sister July begins to assert her own independence. Tension in the family builds on holiday Ireland as a series of surreal encounters test the them all to their limit.
